\f0\b\fs48 \cf0 \strokec2 What is Product Discovery?\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f3\b0\fs24 \cf0 Product Discovery is the continuous process of understanding users, validating problems, testing solutions, and reducing risk before investing significant resources into building a product.\
